  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Associate Engineer",
  "description": "<p>We are looking for a <strong>motivated Associate Engineer</strong> to join our team.</p><p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Assist in site and laboratory testing for construction materials</p></li><li><p>Coordinate with project teams, clients, and site personnel</p></li><li><p>Prepare test reports, records, and related documentation</p></li><li><p>Ensure testing works are carried out in accordance with standards and specifications</p></li><li><p>Support engineers in daily operations and project requirements</p></li><li><p>Perform other duties as assigned</p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Degree in <strong>Civil Engineering or related discipline</strong></p></li><li><p>Fresh graduates are welcome to apply</p></li><li><p>Able to work independently and as part of a team</p></li><li><p>Willing to travel to project sites when required</p></li><li><p>Possess good communication and organisational skills</p></li></ul><p><strong>Added Advantage:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Prior experience in <strong>construction testing, site inspection, or laboratory work</strong></p></li><li><p>Knowledge of Singapore Standards / construction practices</p></li></ul>",
